{"tha-ap401:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap401:0.2":"Pilindavacchavagga ","tha-ap401:0.3":"Sabbadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap401:1.1":"“Mahasamuddam ogayha, ","tha-ap401:1.2":"bhavanam me sunimmitam; ","tha-ap401:1.3":"Sunimmita pokkharani, ","tha-ap401:1.4":"cakkavakapakujita. ","tha-ap401:2.1":"Mandalakehi sanchanna, ","tha-ap401:2.2":"padumuppalakehi ca; ","tha-ap401:2.3":"Nadi ca sandate tattha, ","tha-ap401:2.4":"supatittha manorama. ","tha-ap401:3.1":"Macchakacchapasanchanna, ","tha-ap401:3.2":"nanadijasamotthata; ","tha-ap401:3.3":"Mayurakoncabhiruda, ","tha-ap401:3.4":"kokiladihi vagguhi. ","tha-ap401:4.1":"Parevata ravihamsa ca, ","tha-ap401:4.2":"cakkavaka nadicara; ","tha-ap401:4.3":"Dindibha salika cettha, ","tha-ap401:4.4":"pampaka jivajivaka. ","tha-ap401:5.1":"Hamsa koncapi nadita, ","tha-ap401:5.2":"kosiya pingala bahu; ","tha-ap401:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap401:5.4":"manimuttikavaluka. ","tha-ap401:6.1":"Sabbasonnamaya rukkha, ","tha-ap401:6.2":"nanagandhasamerita; ","tha-ap401:6.3":"Ujjotenti divarattim, ","tha-ap401:6.4":"bhavanam sabbakalikam. ","tha-ap401:7.1":"Satthi turiyasahassani, ","tha-ap401:7.2":"sayam pato pavajjare; ","tha-ap401:7.3":"Solasitthisahassani, ","tha-ap401:7.4":"parivarenti mam sada. ","tha-ap401:8.1":"Abhinikkhamma bhavana, ","tha-ap401:8.2":"sumedham lokanayakam; ","tha-ap401:8.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap401:8.4":"vandayim tam mahayasam. ","tha-ap401:9.1":"Sambuddham abhivadetva, ","tha-ap401:9.2":"sasangham tam nimantayim; ","tha-ap401:9.3":"Adhivasesi so dhiro, ","tha-ap401:9.4":"sumedho lokanayako. ","tha-ap401:10.1":"Mama dhammakatham katva, ","tha-ap401:10.2":"uyyojesi mahamuni; ","tha-ap401:10.3":"Sambuddham abhivadetva, ","tha-ap401:10.4":"bhavanam me upagamim. ","tha-ap401:11.1":"Amantayim parijanam, ","tha-ap401:11.2":"‘sabbe sannipatatha vo; ","tha-ap401:11.3":"Pubbanhasamayam buddho, ","tha-ap401:11.4":"bhavanam agamissati. ","tha-ap401:12.1":"Labha amham suladdham no, ","tha-ap401:12.2":"ye vasama tavantike; ","tha-ap401:12.3":"Mayampi buddhasetthassa, ","tha-ap401:12.4":"pujam kassama satthuno’. ","tha-ap401:13.1":"Annapanam patthapetva, ","tha-ap401:13.2":"kalam arocayim aham; ","tha-ap401:13.3":"Vasisatasahassehi, ","tha-ap401:13.4":"upesi lokanayako. ","tha-ap401:14.1":"Pancangikehi turiyehi, ","tha-ap401:14.2":"paccuggamanamakasaham; ","tha-ap401:14.3":"Sabbasonnamaye pithe, ","tha-ap401:14.4":"nisidi purisuttamo. ","tha-ap401:15.1":"Uparicchadanam asi, ","tha-ap401:15.2":"sabbasonnamayam tada; ","tha-ap401:15.3":"Bijaniyo pavayanti, ","tha-ap401:15.4":"bhikkhusanghassa antare. ","tha-ap401:16.1":"Pahutenannapanena, ","tha-ap401:16.2":"bhikkhusanghamatappayim; ","tha-ap401:16.3":"Paccekadussayugale, ","tha-ap401:16.4":"bhikkhusanghassadasaham. ","tha-ap401:17.1":"Yam vadanti sumedhoti, ","tha-ap401:17.2":"lokahutipatiggaham; ","tha-ap401:17.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap401:17.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap401:18.1":"‘Yo me annena panena, ","tha-ap401:18.2":"sabbe ime ca tappayim; ","tha-ap401:18.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap401:18.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap401:19.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap401:19.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap401:19.3":"Sahassakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap401:19.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap401:20.1":"Upapajjati yam yonim, ","tha-ap401:20.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap401:20.3":"Sabbada sabbasovannam, ","tha-ap401:20.4":"chadanam dharayissati. ","tha-ap401:21.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap401:21.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap401:21.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap401:21.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap401:22.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap401:22.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap401:22.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap401:22.4":"nibbayissatinasavo. ","tha-ap401:23.1":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap401:23.2":"sihanadam nadissati; ","tha-ap401:23.3":"Citake chattam dharenti, ","tha-ap401:23.4":"hettha chattamhi dayhatha’. ","tha-ap401:24.1":"Samannam me anuppattam, ","tha-ap401:24.2":"kilesa jhapita maya; ","tha-ap401:24.3":"Mandape rukkhamule va, ","tha-ap401:24.4":"santapo me na vijjati. ","tha-ap401:25.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap401:25.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap401:25.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap401:25.4":"sabbadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap401:26.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap401:26.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap401:26.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap401:27.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap401:27.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap401:27.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap401:28.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap401:28.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap401:28.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap401:29.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sabbadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap401:30.1":"Sabbadayakattherassapadanam navamam. "}